task.summary: Default task
Initial commit
DICOM to BIDS skeleton
Added mulitiple subject handlers, filename parser, essential file output. Test dataset passes BIDS validator without errors, but many warnings relating to 'a', 'b' etc suffix added by dcm2niix.

Added automatic events.tsv template file generation in func directory. Previous validator warnings due to non-compliant protocol names on console. Need to put _acq key after _task key for _bold series and remove _run key from SE-EPI fieldmap series. Need to open an issue with BIDS GitHub about the fieldmap _run key.
Added template events creation message
Fixed events file overwrite bug
Mostly working version. Need to add more imaging fields to info structure for summary file output.
Rewrote workflow to handle conversion separately for each subject in the DICOM directory. Added template protocol translation dictionary to DICOM root folder to be filled by user for second pass.
Rewrote workflow to handle conversion separately for each subject in the DICOM directory. Added template protocol translation dictionary to DICOM root folder to be filled by user for second pass.
First alpha version. Should work for Conte Core MRI data conversion. Requires user to fill GUIDs manually in each subject's NDAR CSV summary file.
Fixed NDAR summary CSV file column ordering.
Fixed output filename naming for dcm2niix
Added missing NDAR conditional fields. Ready for upload and online validation again.
Limited scan_type string to NDAR valid values (eg "MR Structural (T1)")

Working version which passes online BIDS validator for routine fMRI protocols. Tested against recent Conte Core multiband protocol. Employs 2-pass approach to translating console protocol names to BIDS-compliant names provided by user in a JSON dictionary.
Pre-wide-release alpha version for CIT testing (v0.9.0)
Pre-wide-release alpha version for CIT testing (v0.9.1)
Solution for multiple series with same protocol name (add run-N to BIDS filename to distinguish copies by series number).
Add DICOM header dump to CSV table for multiple DICOM files.
Add DICOM header dump to CSV table for multiple DICOM files.
Add DICOM header dump to CSV table for multiple DICOM files.
Update to latest pydicom. Import name changes from dicom to pydicom
Add alternative heudiconv wrapper (dcm2bids) with CIT-specific heuristic (caltech_bids_heuristic)
Updates to Caltech BIDS heuristic
Rename dcm2bids heudiconv wrapper to heudibids. Session handling updates to dcm2bids.py
More updates to dcm2bids.py
Fixed filename parsing error when subject ID contains one or more dashes.
Fixed filename parsing error when protocol name includes one or more '.'s
Added image_resolution, slice_thickness and slice_timing fields to subject .csv summary. Required by NDAR if not submitting DICOM images.
Added image_resolution, slice_thickness and slice_timing fields to subject .csv summary. Required by NDAR if not submitting DICOM images.
Correct bval/bvec field entries for non-DWI data, add support for slice_orientation
Hardwired orientation for Caltech (sagittal 3D T1 and 3D T2, everything else axial). Removed JSON files after processing.
Latest version works with updated rordenlab/dcm2niix which now includes substantial support for BIDS JSON sidecars.
Update README to reflect integration with latest rordenlab/dcm2niix
Change hashbang to system default python. Remove python 3.2+ makedirs exist_ok flag.
